# Security Policy

## Supported Versions

We actively patch only the most recent minor release. Older versions receive fixes at our discretion.

## Reporting a Vulnerability

Report with an issue with the following items:

- A short summary of the issue
- Steps to reproduce or a proof of concept
- Any logs, stack traces, or screenshots that might help us understand the problem

We acknowledge reports within 48 hours and aim to release a fix or mitigation within 30 days. 

Thank you for helping us keep our users safe.
